<h3 id="矩阵向量形式-matrix-vector-form" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#矩阵向量形式-matrix-vector-form"><span>矩阵向量形式 matrix-vector form</span></a></h3>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><munder><mrow><mi>max</mi><mo>⁡</mo></mrow><mi>π</mi></munder><mrow><mo fence="true">(</mo><msub><mi>r</mi><mi>π</mi></msub><mo>+</mo><mi>γ</mi><msub><mi>P</mi><mi>π</mi></msub><mi>v</mi><mo fence="true">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">v = \max_{\pi} \left( r_{\pi} + \gamma P_{\pi} v \right)
